## Zero-Install Reminder

Treat HarnessForge CLI and Action outputs as advisory unless the repo owner
adopts them as gates. Contributors should use repo-owned docs and checks
without installing HarnessForge.

## Skill Maintenance

When changing this skill or adding repo-local skills:

- Follow Agent Skills spec and best practices:
  `https://agentskills.io/specification.md`;
  `https://agentskills.io/skill-creation/best-practices.md`.
- Use Anthropic's skill-creator as a quality reference:
  `https://github.com/anthropics/skills/tree/main/skills/skill-creator`.
- Keep `SKILL.md` concise; put conditional detail in one-level references.
- Make the description trigger-specific with real tasks and near misses.
- For substantial changes, record 2-3 pressure prompts and compare expected
  behavior with and without the skill.
- Add scripts only for repeated fragile logic or deterministic validation.
